@NODE Incompatibilities "Incompatibilities"
@TOC Main

    If you can't change the screen mode of Workbench while Monitor is running, it is because it doesn't receive a message to hide it's interface, in this case, pause, so it can close the screen.  If you have alot of open drawers, close some and it will go
 faster and allow for a screen mode change.

@ENDNODE


